### Equipment
A new set of equipment is added BP Works shop every patch. The equipment remain in the shop until BP season ends + one more patch.

#### BP Works Vintage
After the BP season ends, **THE EQUIPMENT WILL REMAIN FOR ONE MORE PATCH** in a separate shop called **BP Works Vintage**. This is your last chance to purchase the equipment.
- In Vintage shop, you can convert the new crystallum to the previous crystallum, in case you are short a few crystallum to get an equipment.
